            Live web surfaces and DataCamp pages become source material the moment you export them.
            The bridge between a rendered page and a structured build prompt is shorter than it looks.
          </p>

          <div class="mt-8">
            <a
              href="https://markdown.new/"
              target="_blank"
              rel="noopener noreferrer"
              class="inline-flex items-center rounded-full bg-[#0066cc] px-5 py-2.5 text-[14px] font-normal text-white transition-transform active:scale-95"
              style="font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Helvetica Neue', sans-serif;"
            >
              Try markdown.new →
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Media as Code: pill-h2-bar, cards layout, near-black #272729 -->
