                class="mt-2 text-sm leading-relaxed"
                style="color: #cccccc; font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Helvetica Neue', sans-serif; font-weight: 400;"
              >
                Motion graphics that respond to an audio track — all rendered as HTML, all editable
                as code.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- References: parchment surface -->
      <section class="yil-section bg-[#f5f5f7]">
        <div class="mx-auto max-w-5xl px-6 py-16">
