            References
          </p>
          <div class="mt-6 space-y-4">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
              <span
                class="inline-flex items-center rounded-full border border-[#0066cc]/20 bg-[#0066cc]/10 px-2.5 py-0.5 text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.1em] text-[#0066cc]"
                style="font-family: ui-monospace, SFMono-Regular, Menlo, 'Courier New', monospace; font-weight: 600;"
